OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fabsences 'head on'         
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The education secretary has vowed to   
OL,6, tackle persistent pupil absences "head 
OL,7, on", describing it as a "key priority".
OL,9,FIn a speech to head teachers on        
OL,10,FSaturday, Nadhim Zahawi will say       
OL,11,Fdisadvantaged children lose out most   
OL,12,Ffrom not being in school.              
OL,14,FAhead of the spending review later this
OL,15,Fmonth, he will also pledge to invest   
OL,16,F"record sums" in children's education. 
OL,18,FIt comes after the number of pupils in 
OL,19,FEngland absent for Covid-related       
OL,20,Freasons rose two-thirds in a fortnight.
